    <a title="Ed Fuller" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/7052271-ed-fuller"><img alt="Ed Fuller" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/m_50x66-82093808bca726cb3249a493fbd3bd0f.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
