<span id="freeTextContainer11693109352620966211">What a fantastic book this is. So often you hear of a book that’s supposed to be uplifting or rewarding or whatever, and it ends up being much of a muchness that you’ve read many times before. A Love Story by Samantha Chandler proved to be a real exception and I loved it from start to finish. Great writing combined with such a beautiful story kept me hooked right from the start. Make sure you have time put aside when you start it for yourself, or, if you’re anything like me, you’ll be late for y</span>
  <span id="freeText11693109352620966211" style="display:none">What a fantastic book this is. So often you hear of a book that’s supposed to be uplifting or rewarding or whatever, and it ends up being much of a muchness that you’ve read many times before. A Love Story by Samantha Chandler proved to be a real exception and I loved it from start to finish. Great writing combined with such a beautiful story kept me hooked right from the start. Make sure you have time put aside when you start it for yourself, or, if you’re anything like me, you’ll be late for your next appointment, as you won’t want to put it down.</span>
